OL,3,CHospices 'struggling with demand' to
OL,4,Creceive #4 million in extra funding
OL,6,FJayde Adams and her daughter Savanah
OL,7,Flook forward to their visits to Ty
OL,8,FHafan. Savanah has leukodystrophy
OL,9,Fwhich is a life-limiting brain
OL,10,Fcondition.
OL,12,FMs Adams said: "Savanah coming here is
OL,13,Fthe best thing - she absolutely loves
OL,14,Fit. It gives her that little bit of
OL,15,Findependence and it gives me time to
OL,16,Fcatch-up on sleep and everything I
OL,17,Fneed to do at home.
OL,19,F"It's somewhere to come and people
OL,20,Funderstand us, they know what we're
OL,21,Fgoing through.
