OL,3,CHospices 'struggling with demand' to
OL,4,Creceive #4 million in extra funding
OL,6,F"Ty Hafan do a lot of fundraising to
OL,7,Fbe able to support families like ours
OL,8,Fand I think they do need that little
OL,9,Fbit more support because they go out
OL,10,Fof their way to help families like
OL,11,Fours and where would we be if they
OL,12,Fweren't around?"
OL,14,FHospices traditionally rely on
OL,15,Ffundraising and charitable donations,
OL,16,Fbut the cost-of-living crisis has made
OL,17,Fthis more difficult.
