OL,3,CHospices 'struggling with demand' to
OL,4,Creceive #4 million in extra funding
OL,6,FReduced funding streams have made it
OL,7,Fharder for hospices to retain and
OL,8,Frecruit staff and some have had to
OL,9,Fconsider whether they can continue to
OL,10,Fmaintain services.
OL,12,FDiscussing the funding, Minister for
OL,13,FHealth and Social Services, Eluned
OL,14,FMorgan said: "What this will do I hope
OL,15,Fis to allow them to pay their staff
OL,16,Fthe kind of salaries that are being
OL,17,Fpaid in the NHS.
