OL,3,CHospices 'struggling with demand' to
OL,4,Creceive #4 million in extra funding
OL,6,F"That is crucial for them to retain
OL,7,Fstaff who have this real expertise and
OL,8,Fare absolutely compassionate in the
OL,9,Fway that they work.
OL,11,F"I'm sure that they would want more
OL,12,Fmoney coming to their hospices and I
OL,13,Fquite understand that. The fact that
OL,14,Fthey are helping 20,000 people, very
OL,15,Foften within their homes, means that
OL,16,Fthey're taking a lot of pressure off
OL,17,Fthose NHS beds that are needed for the
OL,18,Furgent cases."
