OL,3,CHospices 'struggling with demand' to
OL,4,Creceive #4 million in extra funding
OL,6,FJason Foster, Interim Chief Executive
OL,7,Fof Ty Hafan Children's Hospice said
OL,8,Fthe money will go a long way in
OL,9,Fhelping hospices provide care but it
OL,10,Fwill not meet the immense demand they
OL,11,Fface.
OL,13,FHe said: "These sums will enable both
OL,14,FTy Gobaith and Ty Hafan to almost
OL,15,Frecord a balanced budget for the 2023-
OL,16,F24 financial year.
OL,18,F"Without this funding, both children's
OL,19,Fhospices would have run at a deficit,
OL,20,Fdrawing on limited funds held in
OL,21,Freserve.
