OL,3,CHospices 'struggling with demand' to
OL,4,Creceive #4 million in extra funding
OL,6,F"However, this funding, while welcome,
OL,7,Fdoes not enable Ty Gobaith and Ty
OL,8,FHafan to meet anything like the demand
OL,9,Ffor the care we provide.
OL,11,F"There are over 3,000 children in
OL,12,FWales who have a life-shortening
OL,13,Fcondition yet between Ty Gobaith and
OL,14,FTy Hafan we are only currently able to
OL,15,Fsupport just over 400 of them."
OL,17,FIt costs #5.7 million per year for Ty
OL,18,FHafan to deliver their care service in
OL,19,Fthe hospice and in the community.
